data.description: Family memories are waiting to be made in this upscale Gulf Front fully furnished 3 bedroom 2 bath residence.  Relax with family and friends on your private balcony as you enjoy the sights and sounds of the Gulf of Mexico.  Among the many features of this residence are upgraded countertops in the kitchen and wet bar area, custom tile flooring in the living room and dining room as well as simulated wood flooring in all 3 bedrooms.  Also included with the purchase of this residence is a 1 year "Home Warranty Plan" for peace of mind.  The Palacio complex offers on site management with a full time maintenance department, beautiful Gulf Front pool and an additional heated lap pool, exercise room with state of the art equipment, community room, lighted tennis courts, under complex parking for a limited number of owners and restricted building access with a front door keypad.  Investment property, second home or primary residence Palacio will exceed your expectations.  Please click on the Virtual Tour link to view the unit.
